{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0fda5b0232","title":"我们在抗战过程中的总方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d85a868097","index":0,"year":1938,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"0fda5b0232"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c0b8c18d78","type":"paragraph","text":"我们在抗战过程中的总方针口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"0fda5b0232"},{"id":"21d2907ba9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年8月6日）陈、周、博、凯、叶：保卫武汉，重在发动民众，军事则重在袭击政人之侧后，退港故进，争取时间，务须避免不利的决战，至事实上不可守时，不情断然放弃之。因目前许多军队的战斗力远不如前，若再损失过大，将增加各将领对蒋中之不满，投降派与割据派起而乘之，有影响蒋的地位及继续抗战之虞。在抗战过程中巩固蒋之地位，坚持抗战，坚决打击投降派，应是我们的总方针。而军队力量之保存，是执行此方针之基础。请加注意为盼","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"0fda5b0232"},{"id":"0694e3c115","type":"paragraph","text":"洛陈康王胡毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"0fda5b0232"},{"id":"5c8298e270","type":"paragraph","text":"鱼[1这是毛泽东和中共中央书记处书记洛前（张闯天）、陈云、康生，中（王明）、周恩来、第古（秦邦光）、凯率（何克全）、叶剑英的电报[2]蒋，播蒋介石。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"0fda5b0232"}],"page":{"id":"79a5545c68","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"0fda5b0232","start":418,"end":418}}}},"__N_SSG":true}